g.text: - The UI has 7 cards and it has to filter only 3 cards
so reconciliation algorithm first create the VIRTUAL DOM
DOM is the actual document object model that exists
in the browser, while virtual DOM is a lightweight DOM
tree constructed in memory. Directly manipulating the DOM
may be slow, while using virtual DOM can improve performance
because virtual DOM updates only the changed parts.
The virtual dom is representation of actual dom.
- The Diff algo is compare the 2 virtual dom.
and the dom with new one. It's make the react fast
because it does not update entire dom it just update
updated nodes which it found in the another dom.
